data.text:
The Big House

Barney Fife becomes super-efficient in executing his duties as deputy sheriff, after two thieves are jailed in Mayberry until their accomplices are captured.

The Case of the Greek Goddess

Perry Mason defends an old friend, a world famous sculptor, charged with murdering a Greek immigrant.

The Boys

Murder and robbery disrupt life in Dodge City when a crooked elixir salesman and his three outlaw sons move in.

Crooked Mile

Quint Asper's life is threatened by the domineering father of the girl he loves.
